Please educate me why.  I&#x27;m not being funny, I truly don&#x27;t understand.<p>I understand some cases:
* Need for offline;
* Need to work like an IM (instant updates pushed from a server, like a telephone / IM / email service);
* Need to avoid latency in user experience (a native game, vs a web-based flash-style game).<p>But I don&#x27;t understand any others, and really would like to know.
